Section 1:
132nd MAINE LEGISLATURE
FIRST REGULAR SESSION-2025
Legislative Document No. 605
An Act to Provide Solutions for Sustainable Management of
Municipal Solid Waste
Received by the Clerk of the House on February 20, 2025. Referred to the Committee on
Environment and Natural Resources pursuant to Joint Rule 308.2 and ordered printed pursuant
to Joint Rule 401.
ROBERT B. HUNT
Clerk
Presented by Representative CAMPBELL of Orrington.
Printed on recycled paper
1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 CONCEPT DRAFT
3 SUMMARY
44 This bill is a concept draft pursuant to Joint Rule 208.
5 This bill proposes to eliminate provisions of law that impede innovative solutions to
6 solid waste disposal and support alternative methods of solid waste disposal, such as reuse
7 and recycling, to reduce volumes in landfills and provide solutions for sustainable
8 management of municipal solid waste.
Page 1 - 132LR0007(01)
